1. *Padne* joj pismo na pod. (The letter fell to the ground.)
2. Nešto će mu *padne* na pamet. (Something will occur to him.)
3. Čim se vidiš sa njom, *padne* ti na pamet. (As soon as you see her, it will come to mind.)
4. *Padne* mu na pamet da joj to kaže. (It will occur to him to tell her that.)
5. *Padne* mu na pamet da je prevariti. (It will occur to him to deceive her.)
6. *Padne* mu teška odluka da napusti dom. (He will have a hard decision to leave home.)